      "text": {
        "text": "*Google Gemini API Shut Down Gemini 2.0 Flash Models*\n`high` `model_retirement` `2026-06-01`\nGoogle Gemini API changelog records the June 1, 2026 shutdown of Gemini 2.0 Flash and Gemini 2.0 Flash-Lite model IDs on the Gemini API surface.\nRefs: provider:google",
        "type": "mrkdwn"
      },
      "type": "section"
    },
    {
      "type": "divider"
    },
    {
      "text": {
        "text": "*Google Vertex AI Retires Gemini 2.0 Flash Stable Models*\n`medium` `model_retirement` `2026-06-01`\nGoogle Vertex AI model-version documentation lists Gemini 2.0 Flash stable model IDs with a June 1, 2026 retirement date and points developers toward newer Gemini stable models.\nRefs: provider:google",
        "type": "mrkdwn"
      },
      "type": "section"
    },
    {
      "type": "divider"
    },
    {
      "text": {
        "text": "*Google Gemini API Shut Down Gemini 3.1 Flash-Lite Preview*\n`medium` `model_retirement` `2026-05-25`\nGoogle Gemini API changelog records the shutdown of the Gemini 3.1 Flash-Lite preview model and directs developers to the generally available Gemini 3.1 Flash-Lite model.\nRefs: provider:google",
        "type": "mrkdwn"
      },
      "type": "section"
    },
    {
      "type": "divider"
    },
    {
      "text": {
        "text": "*Azure OpenAI Retires Legacy GPT-3 Model IDs*\n`medium` `model_retirement` `2024-06-14`\nMicrosoft Learn lists legacy Azure OpenAI GPT-3, Codex, and first-generation embedding model IDs as retired, with replacement guidance for newer instruct and embedding models.\nRefs: provider:azure-openai",
        "type": "mrkdwn"
      },
      "type": "section"
    },
    {
      "type": "divider"
    },
    {
      "text": {
        "text": "*OpenAI Retires Older GPT-3 Completions Models*\n`medium` `model_retirement` `2024-01-04`\nOpenAI retired older GPT-3 completions-era model IDs and first-generation embedding models, requiring applications that still referenced those IDs to migrate to replacement models.\nRefs: provider:openai",
        "type": "mrkdwn"
      },
      "type": "section"
    }
  ],
